show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: Yara was tricked into having a child with Yusuf, but her sister Yulia took the baby and lied about its death. Years later, Yara returns and reunites with Yusuf and the child. When Yulia's abuse of the child is uncovered, she causes a car accident in a panic. Yusuf then learns that Yara is the biological mother, and the family comes together to live happily.
